    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it was first sold. With a flawless exterior and an interior that still smells brand new, it's a rare find for anyone seeking showroom perfection. This is truly a top-tier ride for a discerning driver!",
