    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This beauty has been my pride and joy and is still in wonderful shape! It runs super smoothly and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures. It\u2019s been really well-loved and well-maintained, making it the perfect dependable choice for your daily drives. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make its next owner very happy. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
