      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and analog feedback. This example is mechanically robust, with documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension has been maintained with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the chassis's legendary 50/50 balance. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited use, the drivetrain and VANOS system are dialed in for peak performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
