    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only minor signs of careful use typical of a well-loved car, such as light stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary featuring supple leather seating, pristine carpets, and a fully functional suite of electronics. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly; the engine delivers consistent power, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. Recent service includes a full synthetic oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it\u2019s road-ready from day one. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality driver that has been treated with genuine respect and regular care, this car is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
